Title: 13.1.2 Integer Types (Exact Value) - INTEGER, INT, SMALLINT, TINYINT, MEDIUMINT, BIGINT
Description: A medium-sized integer. The signed range is -8388608 to 8388607. The unsigned range is 0 to 16777215.
Type: MEDIUMINT; Storage (Bytes): 3; Minimum Value Signed: -8388608; Maximum Value Signed: 8388607; Minimum Value Unsigned: 0; Maximum Value Unsigned: 16777215
